 Rita Okoye It has been confirmed that Banky W and Adesua Etomi’s white wedding will take place in South Africa this weekend. The couple who had a lavish traditional wedding on Sunday, November 19, and their private civil ceremony on Monday, have flown out of Nigeria to Cape Town to finalize plans for their wedding which is holding this Weekend. “….And we’re off to Capetown #mySAexperience #BAAD2017 #Finalstep #tooexcited #ohmylawddd ???,” the excited new bride, Adesua captioned a photo she shared.